Paper: hep-th/9404045

Date: 1994-04-07

Title: Exact Solution of 2D Poincare Gravity Coupled to Fermion Matter

Authors: S.N.Solodukhin

Comments: Preprint JINR E2-94-117, 15p., Latex

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D51 (1995) 603-608

The 2D model of gravity with zweibeins $e^{a}$ and the Lorentz connectionone-form $\omega^{a}_{\ b}$ as independent gravitational variables coupled to2d massless Dirac matter is considered. It is shown that the classicalequations of motion are exactly integrated in the case of chiral fermions.